1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:10,000
[English subtitles are available]

2
00:01:36,500 --> 00:01:45,020
[Melody of Golden Age]
[EP27]

3
00:01:54,360 --> 00:01:55,160
Guards!

4
00:01:58,440 --> 00:01:59,560
Give my order:

5
00:02:00,480 --> 00:02:01,920
I am deeply grieved

6
00:02:02,280 --> 00:02:03,720
by the death of Sima Biqiu.

7
00:02:03,960 --> 00:02:06,160
[Investigate this matter thoroughly.]

8
00:02:06,320 --> 00:02:07,320
[From today on,]

9
00:02:07,520 --> 00:02:08,600
lock down the city,

10
00:02:08,600 --> 00:02:10,200
and no one is to leave.

11
00:02:10,200 --> 00:02:12,080
I'll interrogate the suspicious myself.

12
00:02:12,280 --> 00:02:13,080
Yes, Sir.

13
00:02:22,960 --> 00:02:24,400
My lord, thank you

14
00:02:24,720 --> 00:02:25,760
[for helping Biqiu]

15
00:02:25,880 --> 00:02:27,600
[free from his suffering.]

16
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:30,640
Today,

17
00:02:31,160 --> 00:02:32,040
I still have to go to Nanshan

18
00:02:32,040 --> 00:02:33,360
to console his family.

19
00:02:35,480 --> 00:02:36,200
His father has been

20
00:02:36,200 --> 00:02:37,840
raising pigeons there all his life.

21
00:02:38,920 --> 00:02:39,760
[And now,]

22
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:42,200
[he would have to bury his own son.]

23
00:02:43,040 --> 00:02:44,000
After I return,

24
00:02:44,560 --> 00:02:45,600
we can further discuss how to

25
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:48,320
[take down the masked spectre.]

26
00:02:49,000 --> 00:02:50,120
Lord Mo, my condolences.

27
00:02:57,920 --> 00:02:58,840
Raising pigeons?

28
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,080
[I fear that]

29
00:03:01,240 --> 00:03:03,480
Mo Qianzhi, the magistrate of Yingzhou,

30
00:03:03,480 --> 00:03:04,680
might have treacherous intentions, thus

31
00:03:04,920 --> 00:03:07,320
[I command you to secretly investigate.]

32
00:03:07,440 --> 00:03:09,440
Once the red carrier pigeon arrives,

33
00:03:09,600 --> 00:03:11,080
you can send your message.

34
00:03:12,560 --> 00:03:13,680
[Could Biqiu]

35
00:03:14,480 --> 00:03:15,400
[have been a spy planted by]

36
00:03:15,400 --> 00:03:16,960
[the Empress Dowager in Yingzhou?]

37
00:03:17,800 --> 00:03:18,600
[Was Biqiu]

38
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:21,400
[the middleman for my secret messages?]

39
00:03:30,840 --> 00:03:31,640
It's okay now.

40
00:03:33,600 --> 00:03:34,400
What's wrong?

41
00:03:37,160 --> 00:03:37,960
I think

42
00:03:40,480 --> 00:03:42,720
I know why Biqiu was killed,

43
00:03:45,040 --> 00:03:46,280
but I can't tell you.

44
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,080
It's okay.

45
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:58,440
You don't have to if you don't want to.

46
00:04:03,520 --> 00:04:04,320
Shen Du,

47
00:04:06,240 --> 00:04:07,840
do you trust me?

48
00:04:11,880 --> 00:04:13,120
If one day,

49
00:04:14,640 --> 00:04:16,000
I stood against

50
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,320
your dearest one,

51
00:04:20,560 --> 00:04:22,200
would you still trust me?

52
00:04:37,760 --> 00:04:39,000
Aren't you my

53
00:04:43,800 --> 00:04:44,880
dearest one?

54
00:05:18,200 --> 00:05:19,000
I apologize.

55
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:20,680
So it looks like this lead was wrong.

56
00:05:21,200 --> 00:05:22,240
The lead claimed the masked spectres

57
00:05:22,320 --> 00:05:24,680
had been spotted outside the city,

58
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,360
but there's not a soul in sight,

59
00:05:26,440 --> 00:05:27,720
let alone the masked spectres.

60
00:05:35,480 --> 00:05:36,280
Sir,

61
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:38,080
if I may ask,

62
00:05:38,560 --> 00:05:39,960
what's going on today?

63
00:05:40,280 --> 00:05:41,840
Why isn't there

64
00:05:42,200 --> 00:05:43,320
even a street vendor

65
00:05:43,320 --> 00:05:44,120
anywhere in the city?

66
00:05:44,560 --> 00:05:45,360
[Young man,]

67
00:05:45,560 --> 00:05:47,000
[you must be from out of town, right?]

68
00:05:47,120 --> 00:05:48,360
[What terrible timing.]

69
00:05:48,360 --> 00:05:49,320
Just yesterday morning,

70
00:05:49,320 --> 00:05:50,240
the masked spectre

71
00:05:50,240 --> 00:05:51,920
killed Mr. Biqiu at the yamen.

72
00:05:53,160 --> 00:05:55,000
I heard the scene was gruesome.

73
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:56,560
[He was even skinned!]

74
00:05:56,640 --> 00:05:58,040
[No one dares to come out anymore.]

75
00:05:58,440 --> 00:05:59,240
[I only came out]

76
00:05:59,240 --> 00:06:00,640
[because I had to bring some medicine]

77
00:06:00,640 --> 00:06:01,720
[to my mother outside the city.]

78
00:06:02,360 --> 00:06:03,320
I really should get going now.

79
00:06:05,480 --> 00:06:06,640
Only we

80
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:07,920
[and a few people]

81
00:06:07,920 --> 00:06:09,160
at the yamen

82
00:06:09,200 --> 00:06:09,840
knew about the murder

83
00:06:09,840 --> 00:06:11,200
at around 3 a.m.

84
00:06:11,240 --> 00:06:12,480
How did the public

85
00:06:12,560 --> 00:06:13,960
find out about this?

86
00:06:13,960 --> 00:06:15,240
This is indeed suspicious.

87
00:06:15,800 --> 00:06:17,440
[If no one had deliberately spread it,]

88
00:06:17,760 --> 00:06:19,200
[how could a large city like Yingzhou]

89
00:06:19,360 --> 00:06:20,600
have learned about it

90
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:22,560
and turned into a ghost town in a day?

91
00:06:28,200 --> 00:06:28,960
Lady Yan,

92
00:06:28,960 --> 00:06:29,720
the chief has a message for you.

93
00:06:29,720 --> 00:06:30,120
The masked spectre

94
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:31,320
is holding civilians hostage at the gates.

95
00:06:31,320 --> 00:06:32,640
[Please go there quickly.]

96
00:06:39,160 --> 00:06:40,680
Like a moth to a flame,

97
00:06:40,840 --> 00:06:42,760
it perishes instantly.

98
00:06:42,880 --> 00:06:44,880
[No reincarnation is involved,]

99
00:06:45,000 --> 00:06:47,040
yet immortality remains.

100
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:48,440
What are they doing?

101
00:06:48,520 --> 00:06:50,600
They're doing witchcraft.

102
00:06:57,360 --> 00:06:58,160
My lord.

103
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:04,280
[Good.]

104
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:06,840
Everyone's here.

105
00:07:07,320 --> 00:07:08,200
Now,

106
00:07:08,200 --> 00:07:09,960
I will perform how to eat people.

107
00:07:11,920 --> 00:07:13,280
That's Machete of Western Regions,

108
00:07:13,640 --> 00:07:15,800
the weapon that beheaded Li Kaixiang.

109
00:07:16,280 --> 00:07:17,080
[Masked Spectre,]

110
00:07:17,360 --> 00:07:18,680
what do you want?

111
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:21,760
I offer this to you, gods,

112
00:07:21,920 --> 00:07:23,360
and I seek your blessings!

113
00:07:26,360 --> 00:07:27,160
Masked Spectre, if

114
00:07:27,360 --> 00:07:28,600
you don't want to die a gruesome death,

115
00:07:28,600 --> 00:07:29,680
then let them go!

116
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,400
Stop!

117
00:07:31,920 --> 00:07:33,080
What exactly do you want?

118
00:07:33,800 --> 00:07:34,840
Mo Qianzhi,

119
00:07:35,000 --> 00:07:36,080
you came just in time.

120
00:07:36,560 --> 00:07:38,360
The Three Yang's Day is coming soon.

121
00:07:38,400 --> 00:07:39,520
Let these women go!

122
00:07:39,920 --> 00:07:40,920
Let's talk.

123
00:07:41,920 --> 00:07:42,720
Sure.

124
00:07:43,240 --> 00:07:45,160
Then let's see how sincere you are.

125
00:07:45,400 --> 00:07:46,760
[If you agree to]

126
00:07:46,760 --> 00:07:47,520
[stop investigating]

127
00:07:47,520 --> 00:07:49,200
[the masked spectre case from today on,]

128
00:07:49,200 --> 00:07:50,440
I will let them go.

129
00:07:50,960 --> 00:07:52,320
If you refuse,

130
00:07:52,520 --> 00:07:53,720
[then the entire Yingzhou]

131
00:07:53,720 --> 00:07:55,040
will become a ghost town!

132
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:55,960
Shut up!

133
00:07:56,640 --> 00:07:58,080
How dare you be so audacious!

134
00:07:58,520 --> 00:08:00,080
Biqiu was devoted to the people,

135
00:08:00,280 --> 00:08:01,680
as everyone in Yingzhou knows.

136
00:08:01,920 --> 00:08:03,600
[Yet you mercilessly murdered him,]

137
00:08:03,720 --> 00:08:04,880
[skinned him,]

138
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:06,840
and tortured him endlessly.

139
00:08:06,840 --> 00:08:08,800
You are utterly ruthless!

140
00:08:09,840 --> 00:08:11,520
So you don't agree then.

141
00:08:11,520 --> 00:08:13,240
Do you want everyone in the city dead

142
00:08:13,240 --> 00:08:14,320
or what?

143
00:08:14,480 --> 00:08:15,280
Kill them!

144
00:08:24,240 --> 00:08:25,040
Damn it.

145
00:08:25,080 --> 00:08:25,880
Kill them all!

146
00:08:29,080 --> 00:08:29,880
Close the gates!

147
00:08:29,880 --> 00:08:30,640
Release the arrows!

148
00:08:53,600 --> 00:08:54,400
Pan Chi!

149
00:08:56,400 --> 00:08:57,200
Qianzhi,

150
00:08:57,320 --> 00:08:58,880
[don't! Stop!]

151
00:09:00,040 --> 00:09:01,600
The Masked Spectre harms the innocent.

152
00:09:01,960 --> 00:09:02,960
[He must be killed!]

153
00:09:04,280 --> 00:09:05,080
How is he?

154
00:09:05,400 --> 00:09:06,200
Much alive.

155
00:09:07,920 --> 00:09:08,720
This dart is poisonous.

156
00:09:08,720 --> 00:09:09,800
We need to stop the bleeding now.

157
00:09:11,800 --> 00:09:12,800
You stay here.

158
00:09:13,120 --> 00:09:14,200
Don't come out no matter what.

159
00:09:21,280 --> 00:09:22,200
Hold on.

160
00:09:25,480 --> 00:09:26,560
Pan Chi, hold on.

161
00:09:28,320 --> 00:09:29,360
Pan Chi, stay with me.

162
00:09:32,440 --> 00:09:33,520
[Wake up!]

163
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:34,880
Pan Chi.

164
00:09:35,320 --> 00:09:36,600
Pan Chi, wake up.

165
00:09:39,400 --> 00:09:41,400
Pan Chi! Pan Chi!

166
00:09:46,760 --> 00:09:47,640
I never thought

167
00:09:48,200 --> 00:09:49,240
one day you would be

168
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:50,600
holding a sword to my neck.

169
00:09:53,120 --> 00:09:54,080
Order them to stop the arrows.

170
00:09:54,800 --> 00:09:55,880
I'm afraid I can't.

171
00:09:56,680 --> 00:09:57,680
Now there's finally a chance

172
00:09:57,680 --> 00:09:58,920
to take out the Masked Spectre,

173
00:09:58,920 --> 00:10:00,280
how could I let him go?

174
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:01,480
For the people in Yingzhou,

175
00:10:01,520 --> 00:10:03,080
I'd rather wrongful kill than to let him go.

176
00:10:03,080 --> 00:10:04,080
If I kill anyone innocent,

177
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:06,200
I'm willing to repay with my life!

178
00:10:06,200 --> 00:10:08,400
Killing an official incurs death penalty.

179
00:10:08,440 --> 00:10:09,520
My lord,

180
00:10:09,800 --> 00:10:11,520
don't threaten me with the death penalty.

181
00:10:11,600 --> 00:10:12,960
I put the people first

182
00:10:13,080 --> 00:10:14,440
and want to take down the Masked Spectre

183
00:10:14,560 --> 00:10:16,280
to return peace to them.

184
00:10:16,320 --> 00:10:18,000
I would say the same thing

185
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:19,280
even in front of Her Highness.

186
00:10:19,280 --> 00:10:20,480
Open your eyes and see!

187
00:10:20,720 --> 00:10:22,520
Is this the result you want?

188
00:10:24,000 --> 00:10:25,240
[If Xiuxiu were here,]

189
00:10:25,640 --> 00:10:26,720
would she want to

190
00:10:26,720 --> 00:10:28,480
see you like this?

191
00:10:30,200 --> 00:10:31,440
Xiuxiu...

192
00:10:38,240 --> 00:10:39,400
Stop the arrows!

193
00:10:51,200 --> 00:10:52,000
Xing.

194
00:11:21,280 --> 00:11:22,400
[Guangchun Hall?]

195
00:11:24,200 --> 00:11:26,200
This is the Fire Moth Sect's headquarters?

196
00:11:37,640 --> 00:11:38,920
Good.

197
00:11:52,720 --> 00:11:53,880
It's really you.

198
00:11:54,280 --> 00:11:55,120
[Ji Dafu,]

199
00:11:55,920 --> 00:11:57,800
first, you killed Li Kaixiang,

200
00:11:58,160 --> 00:11:59,800
then framed Li Kairui for it,

201
00:12:00,080 --> 00:12:01,280
and now you're using Liu Zongyuan

202
00:12:01,280 --> 00:12:02,280
as a scapegoat.

203
00:12:02,440 --> 00:12:04,080
What are you really up to?

204
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:06,160
I didn't frame Li Kairui.

205
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:08,520
I even paid to help him clear his name.

206
00:12:08,880 --> 00:12:10,320
As for Li Kaixiang,

207
00:12:11,160 --> 00:12:12,720
so what if I killed him?

208
00:12:14,160 --> 00:12:15,200
He deserved to die,

209
00:12:15,520 --> 00:12:17,000
so did Liu Zongyuan.

210
00:12:17,040 --> 00:12:18,280
Those foolish commoners.

211
00:12:18,280 --> 00:12:19,640
They are not worth grieving over.

212
00:12:19,840 --> 00:12:20,640
Perhaps you are

213
00:12:20,640 --> 00:12:21,880
the most foolish of all.

214
00:12:22,080 --> 00:12:23,040
[The people you've killed]

215
00:12:23,040 --> 00:12:24,080
[were all innocent.]

216
00:12:24,320 --> 00:12:25,560
You were a son and a husband.

217
00:12:25,560 --> 00:12:27,160
You also have parents and a wife.

218
00:12:28,040 --> 00:12:29,840
[Do you know how painful it is]

219
00:12:29,840 --> 00:12:31,040
to lose a loved one?

220
00:12:31,320 --> 00:12:32,120
Shut up.

221
00:12:34,120 --> 00:12:35,480
How could I not know

222
00:12:36,760 --> 00:12:37,640
the pain

223
00:12:37,640 --> 00:12:39,600
of losing a loved one?

224
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:45,280
But when I saw Xiulian,

225
00:12:46,600 --> 00:12:49,160
she... she was barely recognizable,

226
00:12:50,440 --> 00:12:52,280
completely mutilated.

227
00:12:58,920 --> 00:13:00,240
But they had promised me

228
00:13:00,240 --> 00:13:01,640
they would bring Xiulian back to life!

229
00:13:01,640 --> 00:13:03,040
She will be back!

230
00:13:03,120 --> 00:13:04,040
Who are they?

231
00:13:04,080 --> 00:13:04,880
They promised you

232
00:13:04,880 --> 00:13:06,360
they would bring Xiulian back to life?

233
00:13:08,400 --> 00:13:09,200
It's a pity

234
00:13:09,840 --> 00:13:11,200
[that you don't look like her.]

235
00:13:11,360 --> 00:13:12,240
[So I'll just]

236
00:13:12,240 --> 00:13:13,640
take you organs.

237
00:13:39,600 --> 00:13:40,400
Shen Du.

238
00:13:42,160 --> 00:13:42,960
Yan Xing,

239
00:13:44,280 --> 00:13:45,080
are you okay?

240
00:13:45,640 --> 00:13:46,440
I'm okay.

241
00:13:46,640 --> 00:13:48,080
How did you find here?

242
00:13:48,080 --> 00:13:49,520
The Masked Spectre's lost a piece of

243
00:13:49,720 --> 00:13:51,160
his clothes during the fight,

244
00:13:51,200 --> 00:13:52,720
[and it had a strong medicinal smell.]

245
00:13:52,720 --> 00:13:53,400
[It reminded me of the place in]

246
00:13:53,400 --> 00:13:54,800
[Yingzhou with the most abundant herbs,]

247
00:13:54,800 --> 00:13:55,320
[which is also]

248
00:13:55,320 --> 00:13:56,520
[the least likely to be suspected-]

249
00:13:56,680 --> 00:13:57,520
[Guangchun Hall.]

250
00:13:57,920 --> 00:13:58,720
Let's get out of here.

251
00:14:01,720 --> 00:14:02,600
What's that?

252
00:14:12,760 --> 00:14:13,560
Snakes!

253
00:14:31,920 --> 00:14:32,880
Shen Du, watch out!

254
00:14:55,840 --> 00:14:56,760
No matter when,

255
00:14:57,440 --> 00:14:59,000
don't you dare get hurt for me.

256
00:15:06,480 --> 00:15:07,280
Shen Du,

257
00:15:07,760 --> 00:15:08,800
thank you for saving me.

258
00:15:09,360 --> 00:15:10,320
When we get out,

259
00:15:10,560 --> 00:15:11,440
I will

260
00:15:11,440 --> 00:15:12,400
be your real wife.

261
00:15:44,800 --> 00:15:46,400
Did you bring the money I asked for?

262
00:15:46,520 --> 00:15:47,240
The sooner

263
00:15:47,240 --> 00:15:48,720
I can get out of Yingzhou safely,

264
00:15:49,000 --> 00:15:50,400
the sooner you can relax.

265
00:15:50,400 --> 00:15:52,080
The money is ready.

266
00:15:53,120 --> 00:15:54,080
I put it at...

267
00:16:04,680 --> 00:16:05,480
You...

268
00:16:05,480 --> 00:16:06,280
How dare you?

269
00:16:07,440 --> 00:16:09,560
The Lord won't let you off!

270
00:16:09,800 --> 00:16:11,520
I'm afraid you might not live to see it.

271
00:16:13,800 --> 00:16:15,080
Ji Dafu, you murderer,

272
00:16:15,080 --> 00:16:16,080
you won't get away!

273
00:16:16,080 --> 00:16:16,800
Guards!

274
00:16:22,840 --> 00:16:24,400
Lock this criminal in the death cell.

275
00:16:24,800 --> 00:16:25,600
Yes, Sir!

276
00:16:58,080 --> 00:16:59,240
Jing Lin, hurry up!

277
00:16:59,920 --> 00:17:00,720
[The water is almost boiled dry,]

278
00:17:00,720 --> 00:17:01,800
and your meat is still not ready.

279
00:17:02,840 --> 00:17:03,760
What's the hurry?

280
00:17:03,920 --> 00:17:04,680
Don't underestimate

281
00:17:04,680 --> 00:17:06,080
my knife skills.

282
00:17:06,960 --> 00:17:07,760
[Here, kid.]

283
00:17:08,240 --> 00:17:09,440
You're a kid!

284
00:17:39,560 --> 00:17:40,360
[Mr. Pan,]

285
00:17:41,040 --> 00:17:41,920
here is your

286
00:17:42,280 --> 00:17:43,640
[longevity stew,]

287
00:17:43,840 --> 00:17:45,160
[nourishing mutton soup]

288
00:17:45,800 --> 00:17:47,239
and yam and pork congee.

289
00:17:47,640 --> 00:17:48,439
Please enjoy.

290
