583
00:32:42,400 --> 00:32:43,280
[It's not possible.]

584
00:32:43,720 --> 00:32:44,840
It couldn't have failed.

585
00:32:44,880 --> 00:32:46,120
It couldn't have failed!

586
00:32:46,520 --> 00:32:47,520
It's you.

587
00:32:47,680 --> 00:32:49,400
You scared away Xiuxiu's spirit

588
00:32:49,400 --> 00:32:50,920
so she couldn't find the way back.

589
00:32:51,040 --> 00:32:51,840
Shen Du,

590
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:53,600
how can you be so cruel!

591
