595
00:33:04,320 --> 00:33:05,320
Humanity?

596
00:33:13,320 --> 00:33:14,600
Don't judge

597
00:33:14,600 --> 00:33:15,960
unless you've been in my shoes.

598
00:33:16,120 --> 00:33:16,920
[Shen Du,]

599
00:33:17,440 --> 00:33:18,360
[you should know this]

600
00:33:18,680 --> 00:33:20,240
[better than anyone.]

601
00:33:21,480 --> 00:33:23,360
If it were possible to bring back

602
00:33:23,560 --> 00:33:24,360
those who died unjustly,

603
00:33:24,360 --> 00:33:25,520
what would you choose?

604
