was the kindest,

606
00:33:32,720 --> 00:33:34,000
the purest person in the world.

607
00:33:34,840 --> 00:33:35,960
But those vile men

608
00:33:35,960 --> 00:33:37,240
forced her to die.

609
00:33:37,600 --> 00:33:38,400
Mo Xiuxiu

610
