didn't die from illness?

611
00:33:43,400 --> 00:33:44,200
What

612
00:33:47,160 --> 00:33:49,040
really happened to Xiuxiu?

613
00:33:50,000 --> 00:33:51,080
Before Xiuxiu died,

614
00:33:51,680 --> 00:33:52,840
