'why'.

616
00:33:55,160 --> 00:33:57,280
[What did she do which is wrong?]

617
00:34:04,760 --> 00:34:05,880
[Please give us some food.]

618
00:34:06,000 --> 00:34:07,200
Please give us some food.

619
00:34:08,040 --> 00:34:08,840
What's going on?

620
