621
00:34:09,960 --> 00:34:11,440
[some refugees blocked our path.]

622
00:34:16,720 --> 00:34:18,280
Give them some food.

623
00:34:18,280 --> 00:34:18,920
[Yes, Sir.]

624
00:34:20,920 --> 00:34:21,720
Qianzhi,

625
00:34:21,800 --> 00:34:23,160
the closer we get to Yingzhou,

626
00:34:23,280 --> 00:34:24,520
the more refugees we encounter.

627
00:34:24,840 --> 00:34:25,560
In the future,

628
00:34:25,560 --> 00:34:27,320
if you take over Gannan,

629
00:34:27,400 --> 00:34:29,400
