630
00:34:29,400 --> 00:34:30,840
help and protect these refugees

631
00:34:30,840 --> 00:34:32,400
and give them a safe place to live.

632
00:34:32,560 --> 00:34:33,680
My dear sister,

633
00:34:34,400 --> 00:34:36,000
you are too kind.

634
00:34:55,600 --> 00:34:56,440
[Here, Xiuxiu.]

635
00:34:56,440 --> 00:34:57,400
[Welcome!]

636
00:34:58,759 --> 00:34:59,799
Please, come in.

637
00:35:00,359 --> 00:35:01,759
Let's just stay here for the night.

638
00:35:01,759 --> 00:35:03,440
