639
00:35:03,880 --> 00:35:05,000
Come in. Come in.

640
00:35:11,080 --> 00:35:11,880
Miss,

641
00:35:12,040 --> 00:35:13,279
do you not feel unwell?

642
00:35:13,279 --> 00:35:14,040
Let me help you to

