646
00:35:17,920 --> 00:35:19,480
I must bring it back quickly.

647
00:35:19,880 --> 00:35:21,080
You look very kind.

648
00:35:21,240 --> 00:35:22,440
Will you please accompany me a bit?

649
00:35:22,720 --> 00:35:23,520
Okay.

650
00:35:23,600 --> 00:35:24,760
I'll help you get home.

651
00:35:24,920 --> 00:35:25,880
Thank you, Miss.

652
00:35:28,520 --> 00:35:29,320
Let's go.

653
00:35:55,880 --> 00:35:57,400
Help! Help!

654
00:35:57,760 --> 00:35:59,200
I just ran into some bad people.

655
00:35:59,280 --> 00:36:00,840
My family is waiting for me at the station.

656
00:36:00,880 --> 00:36:02,680
Would you please help me get back there?

657
00:36:04,600 --> 00:36:05,440
Don't worry.

658
00:36:05,880 --> 00:36:07,080
I will help you.

659
00:36:07,720 --> 00:36:08,400
Xiuxiu!

660
00:36:08,400 --> 00:36:09,360
Don't come near.

661
00:36:09,880 --> 00:36:10,680
No!

662
00:36:11,200 --> 00:36:11,960
Don't come near!

663
00:36:11,960 --> 00:36:12,560
[Xiuxiu!]

664
00:36:13,400 --> 00:36:13,960
[Xiuxiu!]

665
00:36:15,400 --> 00:36:16,200
It's okay now.

666
00:36:17,920 --> 00:36:18,880
Come back with me.

667
00:36:19,160 --> 00:36:20,480
[No one will hurt you ever again.]

668
00:36:20,480 --> 00:36:21,120
No.

669
00:36:22,200 --> 00:36:23,080
I made a mistake,

670
00:36:23,080 --> 00:36:23,840
Qianzhi.

671
00:36:24,120 --> 00:36:25,680
[But I only wanted to help her.]

672
00:36:26,400 --> 00:36:27,920
What did I do which is wrong?

673
00:36:27,920 --> 00:36:28,640
Xiuxiu.

674
00:36:29,000 --> 00:36:29,800
Xiuxiu!

675
00:36:30,880 --> 00:36:31,360
[No!]

676
00:36:32,480 --> 00:36:33,160
Xiuxiu!

677
00:36:34,120 --> 00:36:35,800
Xiuxiu!

678
00:36:44,040 --> 00:36:44,840
[Qianzhi.]

679
00:37:18,280 --> 00:37:19,120
Who are you?

680
00:37:20,920 --> 00:37:22,320
It doesn't matter who I am.

681
00:37:23,040 --> 00:37:25,440
But if you want to bring back your sister,

682
00:37:25,880 --> 00:37:27,400
I can help you with that.

683
00:37:29,840 --> 00:37:31,440
Bring the dead back to life?

684
00:37:31,920 --> 00:37:33,240
That's absurd.

685
00:37:33,840 --> 00:37:35,000
The world is vast

686
00:37:35,120 --> 00:37:36,320
and full of wonders.

687
00:37:36,680 --> 00:37:38,000
Just because you've not seen it in Cang

688
00:37:38,040 --> 00:37:39,600
[doesn't mean it doesn't exist.]

689
00:37:39,880 --> 00:37:42,600
As long as your heart is sincere enough.

690
00:38:11,800 --> 00:38:12,800
Can you truly

691
00:38:13,240 --> 00:38:14,600
bring the dead back to life?

692
00:38:14,840 --> 00:38:15,680
Of course.

693
00:38:24,240 --> 00:38:25,760
The fire moth rises from the ashes.

694
00:38:26,240 --> 00:38:28,000
That is the essence of the Fire Moth Sect.

695
00:38:28,400 --> 00:38:30,600
[If you wish to follow me,]

696
00:38:30,920 --> 00:38:31,720
then I

697
00:38:32,160 --> 00:38:34,200
can resurrect your sister.

698
00:38:38,360 --> 00:38:40,120
As long as you can bring back Xiuxiu,

699
00:38:40,920 --> 00:38:42,080
I, Mo Qianzhi,

700
00:38:44,000 --> 00:38:45,480
would do anything for you.

701
00:38:48,840 --> 00:38:50,280
[These so-called secrets to resurrection]

702
00:38:51,080 --> 00:38:51,840
