703
00:38:51,840 --> 00:38:53,400
to manipulate people.

704
00:38:54,080 --> 00:38:55,480
You were lost in your obsession.

705
00:38:55,480 --> 00:38:57,000
That's why you believed it.

706
00:38:57,160 --> 00:38:57,960
Qianzhi,

707
00:38:58,880 --> 00:38:59,960
did you really not know

708
00:39:00,960 --> 00:39:02,680
that it was because of your protection

709
00:39:03,800 --> 00:39:05,320
