710
00:39:05,320 --> 00:39:06,560
Gannan for years,

711
00:39:06,560 --> 00:39:08,120
killing countless people?

712
00:39:08,280 --> 00:39:09,240
[How could you still believe]

713
00:39:09,240 --> 00:39:10,720
[they could bring back Mo Xiuxiu?]

714
00:39:10,720 --> 00:39:11,720
Why shouldn't I?

715
00:39:12,880 --> 00:39:14,240
[What reason do I have not to?]

716
00:39:14,920 --> 00:39:16,400
[As long as I can bring back Xiuxiu,]

717
00:39:16,680 --> 00:39:17,960
[what does it matter]

718
00:39:18,120 --> 00:39:19,280
[killing a few more?]

719
00:39:19,920 --> 00:39:21,240
Those bastards,

720
00:39:21,720 --> 00:39:23,280
didn't they deserve to die?

721
00:39:25,200 --> 00:39:27,000
The Masked Spectre of Guangchun Hall

722
00:39:27,400 --> 00:39:28,920
killed them for me.

723
00:39:29,600 --> 00:39:31,240
[Xiuxiu helped those refugees,]

724
00:39:31,240 --> 00:39:32,480
[but then she was humiliated by those]

725
00:39:32,480 --> 00:39:33,600
[vile men and jumped off a cliff.]

726
00:39:33,640 --> 00:39:35,160
[How could I not avenge her for that?]

727
00:39:35,480 --> 00:39:37,400
Help me! Help me!

728
00:39:37,720 --> 00:39:38,480
Someone wants to kill me!

729
00:39:38,480 --> 00:39:38,880
Don't be scared.

730
00:39:38,880 --> 00:39:39,280
Help me!

731
00:39:39,280 --> 00:39:40,080
We are in broad daylight.

732
00:39:40,080 --> 00:39:41,200
Do you have no regard for the law?

733
00:39:41,320 --> 00:39:42,280
Mr. Mo is here.

734
00:39:42,280 --> 00:39:43,320
We will protect you.

735
00:39:43,920 --> 00:39:44,800
It's them.

736
00:39:44,880 --> 00:39:46,120
They want to kill me!

737
00:39:46,120 --> 00:39:47,760
Why do they want to kill you?

738
00:40:00,280 --> 00:40:01,200
Xiuxiu,

739
00:40:02,840 --> 00:40:04,800
I will avenge you.

740
00:40:04,880 --> 00:40:06,240
They all deserved to die!

741
00:40:06,560 --> 00:40:08,160
They should all die for their sin!

742
00:40:08,600 --> 00:40:09,400
[Shen Du, why]

743
00:40:09,720 --> 00:40:11,040
[did you sabotage the sacrificial ritual?]

744
00:40:11,480 --> 00:40:12,320
Why?

745
00:40:12,760 --> 00:40:14,880
You just didn't want Xiuxiu to come back.

746
00:40:14,920 --> 00:40:16,160
Those men deserved to die,

747
00:40:16,840 --> 00:40:17,800
