748
00:40:20,560 --> 00:40:22,000
What did they do which is wrong?

749
00:40:22,440 --> 00:40:24,280
Things are just not fair in this world.

750
00:40:24,880 --> 00:40:25,680
[Shen Du,]

751
00:40:26,200 --> 00:40:27,640
you know that well.

752
00:40:28,000 --> 00:40:29,880
By using others' lives as sacrifices,

753
00:40:30,320 --> 00:40:32,240
