00:41:51,880 --> 00:41:53,640
influenced by the Fire Moth Sect and

771
00:41:53,680 --> 00:41:55,160
was intended for the resurrecting ritual.

772
00:41:56,040 --> 00:41:57,040
Creating mystery.

773
00:41:57,480 --> 00:41:58,440
Spreading fear.

774
00:41:59,720 --> 00:42:01,440
That's how the Fire Moth Sect

775
00:42:02,560 --> 00:42:03,320
maintains control over their followers-

776
00:42:03,320 --> 00:42:05,160
through intimidation and fear.

777
00:42:08,600 --> 00:42:09,400
Xiu.

778
00:42:12,000 --> 00:42:12,800
Be careful.

779
00:42:13,520 --> 00:42:14,320
Careful.

780
00:42:20,320 --> 00:42:21,200
Lady Yan,

